(COMMUNICATION INFRASTRUCTURE FOR CRPF SECTOR OFFICES) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(=======================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 1: NOTICE INVITING TENDER) Tj T*
(=======================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.1 CRPF invites sealed competitive bids from eligible firms for the) Tj T*
(    procurement of integrated communication infrastructure.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.2 Estimated cost: Rs. 45,00,00,000 \(Forty-Five Crore Rupees\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.3 Earnest Money Deposit \(EMD\): Rs. 90,00,000 \(Ninety Lakh Rupees\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1.4 Bid validity: 180 days from date of submission) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(=======================================================================) Tj T*
(SECTION 3: QUALIFICATION / ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA \(MANDATORY\)) Tj T*
(=======================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.1 FINANCIAL QUALIFICATION CRITERIA) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    3.1.1 ANNUAL TURNOVER:) Tj T*
(    The bidder shall have a minimum annual turnover of Rs. 15 crore) Tj T*
(    in each of the last three financial years \(FY 2022-23, FY 2023-24,) Tj T*
(    FY 2024-25\) as evidenced by audited financial statements certified) Tj T*
(    by a Chartered Accountant.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    Documents required: Audited Balance Sheets and Profit & Loss) Tj T*
(    Accounts for FY 2022-23, FY 2023-24, and FY 2024-25.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.2 TECHNICAL QUALIFICATION CRITERIA) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    3.2.1 SIMILAR WORKS EXPERIENCE:) Tj T*
(    The bidder must have successfully executed at least 3 similar projects) Tj T*
(    completed in the last 5 years involving supply and installation of) Tj T*
(    communication or networking equipment for government organizations.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    "Similar project" means any project with a value exceeding Rs. 10 crore) Tj T*
(    involving structured cabling, networking, or communication systems.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    Documents required:) Tj T*
(    - Work Order copies from client) Tj T*
(    - Project Completion Certificates from client organization) Tj T*
(    - Performance certificate indicating satisfactory completion) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3.3 COMPLIANCE CRITERIA \(MANDATORY\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(    3.3.1 GST REGISTRATION:) Tj T*
